OL,3,CWhat do young voters in Wales make of
OL,4,Cproposed National Service?
OL,6,FWith nearly a month to go until the
OL,7,FGeneral Election, many voters may
OL,8,Fstill be deciding which candidate to
OL,9,Fchoose.
OL,11,FSome of those people may be voting for
OL,12,Fthe first time, and all parties will
OL,13,Fbe vying for their vote.
OL,15,FThe Conservatives have pledged to
OL,16,Fintroduce a new National Service for
OL,17,F18-year-olds, where they will either
OL,18,Ftrain in the military for a year, or
OL,19,Fdo a form of community service in
OL,20,Forganisations like the NHS or fire
OL,21,Fservice.
