OL,3,CWhat do young voters in Wales make of
OL,4,Cproposed National Service?
OL,6,FThose who refuse to participate could
OL,7,Fbe subject to "some form of sanction".
OL,9,FThe party said this would create
OL,10,Fopportunities for young people and
OL,11,Fgive them "real world skills".
OL,13,FBut Labour have called the policy a
OL,14,Fgimmick, and Plaid Cymru have called
OL,15,Fit "an attack on the young".
OL,17,FSo what do young people in Wales think
OL,18,Fof the pledge? At one film group in
OL,19,FRhyl, they weren't keen.
