OL,3,CWhat do young voters in Wales make of
OL,4,Cproposed National Service?
OL,6,FDylan Owen, 21, said "I think it's
OL,7,Ftaking away all the opportunities from
OL,8,Fyoung people to get out there and do
OL,9,Ftheir hobbies, because if you're
OL,10,Fmaking them go into the army then
OL,11,Fthey're not getting that opportunity
OL,12,Fto perform.
OL,14,F"They're forcing them in a way."
OL,16,F15-year-old Amy Virgo also disliked
OL,17,Fthe policy, saying "it's the wrong way
OL,18,Fto go about it, because if you want to
OL,19,Fdo it you can, but you don't need to
OL,20,Fbe getting told to do it."
