OL,3,CWhat do young voters in Wales make of
OL,4,Cproposed National Service?
OL,6,F"I just want people to listen to our
OL,7,Fideas."
OL,9,FListening to young people is something
OL,10,FEllie Hughes, 21, was also worried
OL,11,Fabout.
OL,13,FShe said: "Our government doesn't
OL,14,Flisten to young people like me, to
OL,15,Funderstand what we want for our future
OL,16,Fgenerations."
OL,18,FThese young people have a month to
OL,19,Fmake up their minds before they go to
OL,20,Fthe polls on July 4th.
